{"tid":1389601,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家抗爭方式需要認真思考一下","createTime":"2019-07-31T02:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T14:21:10.000Z","uid":236592,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3457c7176864c84a272cedb1af552136b69faa7a","tid":1389601,"uid":236592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:42:48.000Z","msg":"衆所周知，政府希望民眾互鬥消耗民氣，慢慢平息事件，所以大家其實應該反其道而行，針對番個政權。<br />\n<br />\n所以我其實不支持港鐵不合作或光復上水元朗等運動。因為這些運動妨擾到既係普通市民，對上位者根本冇影響。你話想喚醒普通市民？根本要醒既一早已經醒咗，反而會對偏藍既人有反效果，佢更加會認為我們搞搞震，最後就會變成互相指責甚至打鬥。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭者，請做一些真正針對在上位者既事吧。例如去高官大宅野餐，參觀禮賓府，或者去揾777簽名合照。高官行踨才應該是你們最關心的事"},{"pid":"88d20af57d8697908df282e82070feefd5ef9e1d","tid":1389601,"uid":236592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:54:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30c7351f330aba358807842d029fdd322ca9537c","tid":1389601,"uid":236592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:13:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc0a8953ce4388e1d8ae4454d45e1c73655e7ae7","tid":1389601,"uid":56498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30c7351f330aba358807842d029fdd322ca9537c","tid":1389601,"uid":236592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:13:38.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:29:33.000Z","msg":"PISH"},{"pid":"1917ba6b5a263b3827ef5ebe591400e7eefcbf03","tid":1389601,"uid":236592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc0a8953ce4388e1d8ae4454d45e1c73655e7ae7","tid":1389601,"uid":56498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30c7351f330aba358807842d029fdd322ca9537c","tid":1389601,"uid":236592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:13:38.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:29:33.000Z","msg":"PISH"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:21:10.000Z","msg":"謝"}]}